| AKABAK 2.1 Script - Case A: Parallel Bundle Validation
| Driver: 18Sound 12NW100
| Topology: Split-Path Recombination

System 'CaseA'

| --- Driver Definition ---
Def_Driver 'D1'
  Sd=531.00cm2
  Bl=21.30Tm
  Cms=1.50E-04m/N
  Rms=4.10Ns/m
  Re=5.00ohm
  Le=1.40mH
  Mms=94.00g

| --- Network ---

| Correcting to the syntax found in GPXL003.BKS
Source 'G1' Node=1=0
  V=2.83V  Rs=0.00ohm

| Driver connectivity: ElecNodes=1=0, MechNodes=2=3
Driver 'Dr1' Def='D1' Node=1=0=2=3

| Rear Enclosure
Enclosure 'E1' Node=3
  Vb=5.00L  Lb=15.00cm

| --- Parallel Paths ---

| Path 1: Short, narrow
Duct 'Path1' Node=2=4
  Sd=250.00cm2  Len=30.00cm

| Path 2: Long, wider
Duct 'Path2' Node=2=4
  Sd=350.00cm2  Len=45.00cm

| --- Common Exit & Radiation ---

HornSegment 'Exit' Node=4=5
  S1=600.00cm2  S2=800.00cm2  Len=10.00cm  T=1.00

Radiator 'Mouth' Node=5
  Def='Exit'
  Win=2pi  x=0  y=0  z=0
